title: "Cuaderno de patrocinio del personal"
subtitle: "Conozca a las personas detrás del Hospital San Miguel y patrocine una historia."
category_label: "Donar"
slug: "donate/sponsor-booklet"
featured_image: "../../../assets/images/sponsor-booklet/cuaderno-patrocinio-es.jpg"
